(2) Fastx-Toolkit (http://hannonlab.cshl.edu/fastx_toolkit/), which is a collection of command line tools for short-reads FASTA/FASTQ files preprocessing, including read length trimming, identical reads collapsing, adapter removing, format converting, etc.
